This is the repository for transforming antiX Linux into Swift Linux.

To download this repository and other repositories, open a regular user shell and enter:
mkdir ~/develop
cd ~/develop
git clone git@github.com:swiftlinux/1-build.git
cd ~/develop/1-build
sh get_reps_diet.sh

Other important commands:
sh desktop-diet.sh: Transforms the desktop installation of antiX Linux into Diet Swift Linux

sh build-diet.sh: Transforms the antiX Linux ISO file into the Diet Swift Linux ISO file


